171
00:14:02,021 --> 00:14:03,682
"Well, I'm sorry, Your Honor...

172
00:14:03,756 --> 00:14:06,919
"but how was I supposed to know
it was your car?"

173
00:14:08,094 --> 00:14:11,552
- I don't think I could be a public defender.
- No? Why not?

174
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:14,724
