177
00:14:22,441 --> 00:14:26,901
Me? My family owns a business.
Actually, it's a funeral home.

178
00:14:30,316 --> 00:14:33,717
But I got out of that really quickly,
and now I'm in textiles.

179
00:14:35,221 --> 00:14:36,711
I like fabric.

180
00:14:38,557 --> 00:14:41,856
