I have a lot of work...

181
00:14:41,927 --> 00:14:45,693
- Okay. Maybe we'll see each other around.
- David, relax.

182
00:14:45,765 --> 00:14:49,826
It's fine. I understand.
I guess there's not much of a spark here.

183
