but you don't show it as much.

189
00:15:12,758 --> 00:15:14,623
Do you have any extra?

190
00:15:18,831 --> 00:15:22,824
Let's go on a real date next time.
Like, for dinner.

191
00:15:23,435 --> 00:15:25,426
Okay, that would be nice.

192
00:15:28,107 --> 00:15:30,007
You seem a little...

193
00:15:30,376 --> 00:15:34,972
