I open my mouth, I hear my father.

216
00:16:56,395 --> 00:17:00,024
Stop being so hard on yourself.
That child is not easy.

217
00:17:01,066 --> 00:17:04,001
I swore to myself I would never be like him.

218
00:17:10,075 --> 00:17:11,804
I'm not in the mood.

219
00:17:16,248 --> 00:17:17,340
Fine.

220
00:18:05,464 --> 00:18:06,658
<i>Get up!</i>

221
00:18:55,781 --> 00:18:58,875
<i>- Hello?</i>
- Hi, Melissa. It's Brenda.

222
00:18:59,952 --> 00:19:01,180
